dct_title_s: Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Tajikistan, Turkmenistan, Uzbekistan : geographical map / Gizi Map
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Index of places by country on verso. Topographic map of Central Asia emphasizing roads, tracks, footpaths and railroads; international boundaries. Shows Aksay Chin (claimed by India under Chinese administration).
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
